{"data":[{"name":"70:1","price":"請う者が、（自分と自分の民に、復活の日*に）起こるべき懲罰（が下されること）を請うた。¹","arabic":"سَأَلَ سَآئِلُۢ بِعَذَابٖ وَاقِعٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5376,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　これは、懲罰を早く下してみよ、という不信仰者*の挑発的な言葉とされる（アル＝バガウィー５：１５１参照）。家畜章５７－５８、戦利品*章３２、ユーヌス*章５０、フード*章８、雷鳴章６、夜の旅章９２、巡礼*章４７、蜘蛛章５３、サード章１６、相談章１８も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"sa-ala sāilun biʿadhābin wāqiʿin ","translations":["Asked","a questioner","about a punishment","bound to happen","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["sa-ala","sāilun","biʿadhābin","wāqiʿin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,720],[2,720,3789],[3,3789,6089],[4,6089,7264]]}},{"name":"70:2","price":"不信仰者*たちには、それを防いでくれる者など、いない。","arabic":"لِّلۡكَٰفِرِينَ لَيۡسَ لَهُۥ دَافِعٞ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5377,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"lil'kāfirīna laysa lahu dāfiʿun ","translations":["To the disbelievers","not","of it","any preventer","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["lil'kāfirīna","laysa","lahu","dāfiʿun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1730],[2,1730,2520],[3,2520,3080],[4,3080,4395]]}},{"name":"70:3","price":"階段の主¹であられるアッラー*から（、それを防いでくれる者など）。","arabic":"مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ ذِي ٱلۡمَعَارِجِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5378,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　天使*が天へと昇って行く「『階段』の主」のほかにも、「高さの極みと、位階、徳、恩恵を備えたお方」「偉大さと至高性の主」といった解釈がある（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：２８１参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"mina al-lahi dhī al-maʿāriji ","translations":["From","Allah","Owner","(of) the ways of ascent","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["mina","al-lahi","dhī","al-maʿāriji",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1430],[3,1430,1620],[4,1620,2935]]}},{"name":"70:4","price":"天使*たちと魂¹は、その長さが五万年もの日、かれの御許へと昇っていく²。","arabic":"تَعۡرُجُ ٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ وَٱلرُّوحُ إِلَيۡهِ فِي يَوۡمٖ كَانَ مِقۡدَارُهُۥ خَمۡسِينَ أَلۡفَ سَنَةٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5379,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この「魂」には、「ジブリール*」「人間の魂」といった解釈がある（イブン・カスィール８：２２０参照）。 ２　これは一説に「復活の日*」の事。また一説には「地上からアッラー*の御座（高壁章５４とその訳注も参照）までの階段を、彼ら以外であれば五万年かかるところを、一日で昇る」事を指す（イブン・ジャウズィー８：３５９－３６０参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"taʿruju al-malāikatu wal-rūḥu ilayhi fī yawmin kāna miq'dāruhu khamsīna alfa sanatin ","translations":["Ascend","the Angels","and the Spirit","to Him","in","a Day","[is]","its measure","(is) fifty","thousand","year(s)","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["taʿruju","al-malāikatu","wal-rūḥu","ilayhi","fī","yawmin","kāna","miq'dāruhu","khamsīna","alfa","sanatin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,870],[2,870,3970],[3,3970,4970],[4,4970,5780],[5,5780,6210],[6,6210,7900],[7,7900,8480],[8,8480,9920],[9,9920,10990],[10,10990,11580],[11,11580,12765]]}},{"name":"70:5","price":"ならば（使徒*よ、彼らの嘲笑と挑発に）、よき忍耐¹で忍耐*せよ。","arabic":"فَٱصۡبِرۡ صَبۡرٗا جَمِيلًا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5380,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　「よき忍耐*」については、ユースフ*章１８の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-iṣ'bir ṣabran jamīlan ","translations":["So be patient","a patience","good","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-iṣ'bir","ṣabran","jamīlan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,780],[2,780,2270],[3,2270,3965]]}},{"name":"70:6","price":"本当に彼ら（不信仰者*）は、それ（懲罰）があり得ないと思っている。","arabic":"إِنَّهُمۡ يَرَوۡنَهُۥ بَعِيدٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5381,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"innahum yarawnahu baʿīdan ","translations":["Indeed, they","see it","(as) far off","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["innahum","yarawnahu","baʿīdan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1680],[2,1680,2910],[3,2910,4165]]}},{"name":"70:7","price":"そしてわれら*は、それが近い（日に、確実に到来する）ものと見る。","arabic":"وَنَرَىٰهُ قَرِيبٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5382,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wanarāhu qarīban ","translations":["But We see it","near","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wanarāhu","qarīban",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,2705]]}},{"name":"70:8","price":"天が、溶けた鉛のようになる日。","arabic":"يَوۡمَ تَكُونُ ٱلسَّمَآءُ كَٱلۡمُهۡلِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5383,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma takūnu al-samāu kal-muh'li ","translations":["(The) Day ","will be","the sky","like molten copper","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","takūnu","al-samāu","kal-muh'li",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,610],[2,610,1460],[3,1460,3880],[4,3880,5275]]}},{"name":"70:9","price":"また山々が、（解されて散り散りになった、）染められた羊毛のようになる日。¹","arabic":"وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5384,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　復活の日*の天変地異の様子については、洞窟章４７、ター・ハー章１０５－１０７、蟻章８８、山章９－１０、出来事章５－６、衣を纏（まと）う者章１４、真実章１４－１６、消息章２０、巻き込む章３、衝撃章４－５も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"watakūnu al-jibālu kal-ʿih'ni ","translations":["And will be","the mountains","like wool","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["watakūnu","al-jibālu","kal-ʿih'ni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1020],[2,1020,2150],[3,2150,3525]]}},{"name":"70:10","price":"近しい者が、近いしい者について尋ねることもない。¹","arabic":"وَلَا يَسۡـَٔلُ حَمِيمٌ حَمِيمٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5385,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この解釈には、「人はその日、近しい者からの援助を請うことはない。なぜなら彼が何も出来ないことを、知っているからである」「誰しもが自分のことで頭が一杯なため、他人のことを尋ねる余裕もない」といった説がある（イブン・ジュザイ２：４８６参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"walā yasalu ḥamīmun ḥamīman ","translations":["And not","will ask","a friend","(about) a friend","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","yasalu","ḥamīmun","ḥamīman",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1430],[3,1430,2460],[4,2460,4095]]}},{"name":"70:11","price":"彼らには、彼ら¹が見える。（不信仰だった）罪悪者は、自分の子供たちで、その日の懲罰を償えば、と望む。","arabic":"يُبَصَّرُونَهُمۡۚ يَوَدُّ ٱلۡمُجۡرِمُ لَوۡ يَفۡتَدِي مِنۡ عَذَابِ يَوۡمِئِذِۭ بِبَنِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5386,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　二つの「彼ら」については、「いずれも、近しい者たち」「信仰者たちが、地獄にいる不信仰者たちを見せられる」「いずれも不信仰者*だが、前者は追従者たち、後者は指導者たち」「前者は天使*たち、後者は人々」といった説がある（アル＝クルトゥビー１８：２８５－２８６参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yubaṣṣarūnahum yawaddu al-muj'rimu law yaftadī min ʿadhābi yawmi-idhin bibanīhi ","translations":["They will be made to see each other","Would wish","the criminal","if","he (could be) ransomed","from","(the) punishment","(of) that Day","by his children","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["yubaṣṣarūnahum","yawaddu","al-muj'rimu","law","yaftadī","min","ʿadhābi","yawmi-idhin","bibanīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2540],[2,2540,3300],[3,3300,4290],[4,4290,4680],[5,4680,5750],[6,5750,6080],[7,6080,6940],[8,6940,8870],[9,8870,12485]]}},{"name":"70:12","price":"また自分の配偶者、兄弟、","arabic":"وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَأَخِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5387,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waṣāḥibatihi wa-akhīhi ","translations":["And his spouse","and his brother","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["waṣāḥibatihi","wa-akhīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1810],[2,1810,4775]]}},{"name":"70:13","price":"自分を匿ってくれる近親、","arabic":"وَفَصِيلَتِهِ ٱلَّتِي تُـٔۡوِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5388,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wafaṣīlatihi allatī tu'wīhi ","translations":["And his nearest kindred","who","sheltered him","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["wafaṣīlatihi","allatī","tu'wīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1570],[2,1570,2420],[3,2420,5215]]}},{"name":"70:14","price":"そして地上の全ての者（によって自らの懲罰を償うこと）で、（その代償が）自分を救ってくれることを（望む）。","arabic":"وَمَن فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ جَمِيعٗا ثُمَّ يُنجِيهِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5389,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"waman fī al-arḍi jamīʿan thumma yunjīhi ","translations":["And whoever","(is) on","the earth","all","then","it (could) save him","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["waman","fī","al-arḍi","jamīʿan","thumma","yunjīhi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1190],[2,1190,1440],[3,1440,2260],[4,2260,4089],[5,4089,5439],[6,5439,9824]]}},{"name":"70:15","price":"断じて（、そんなことは役に立た）ない！実にそれ（地獄）は燃え盛るもの。","arabic":"كَلَّآۖ إِنَّهَا لَظَىٰ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5390,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innahā laẓā ","translations":["By no means","Indeed, it (is)","surely a Flame of Hell","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","innahā","laẓā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2550],[2,2550,4360],[3,4360,5575]]}},{"name":"70:16","price":"（それは、）身体の各部¹をもぎ取る。","arabic":"نَزَّاعَةٗ لِّلشَّوَىٰ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5391,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　「身体の各部」の解釈には、ほかにも「頭皮」「骨以外の肉」「顔の重要な部分」といった諸説がある（アル＝バガウィー５：１５３参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"nazzāʿatan lilshawā ","translations":["A remover","of the skin of the head","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["nazzāʿatan","lilshawā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1410],[2,1410,2775]]}},{"name":"70:17","price":"それは、招くのである。（現世での真理に）背を向け、（アッラー*とその使徒*への服従から）背き去り、","arabic":"تَدۡعُواْ مَنۡ أَدۡبَرَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5392,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"tadʿū man adbara watawallā ","translations":["Inviting","(him) who","turned his back","and went away","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["tadʿū","man","adbara","watawallā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,850],[2,850,1240],[3,1240,2130],[4,2130,3475]]}},{"name":"70:18","price":"（財産を）かき集めては、（そこにおけるアッラー*への義務も果たすことなく、）貯めこんだ者を。","arabic":"وَجَمَعَ فَأَوۡعَىٰٓ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5393,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wajamaʿa fa-awʿā ","translations":["And collected","and hoarded","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["wajamaʿa","fa-awʿā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,880],[2,880,2125]]}},{"name":"70:19","price":"本当に人間は、せっかちに創られた。","arabic":"۞ إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ خُلِقَ هَلُوعًا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5394,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna al-insāna khuliqa halūʿan ","translations":["Indeed","the man","was created","anxious ","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","al-insāna","khuliqa","halūʿan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1300],[2,1300,3260],[3,3260,3960],[4,3960,5595]]}},{"name":"70:20","price":"悪が自分に降りかかれば、ひどく取り乱し、","arabic":"إِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلشَّرُّ جَزُوعٗا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5395,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā massahu al-sharu jazūʿan ","translations":["When","touches him","the evil","distressed","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","massahu","al-sharu","jazūʿan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1350],[3,1350,2160],[4,2160,3755]]}},{"name":"70:21","price":"善が自分に降りかかれば、強欲になる。","arabic":"وَإِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلۡخَيۡرُ مَنُوعًا","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5396,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā massahu al-khayru manūʿan ","translations":["And when","touches him","the good","withholding","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","massahu","al-khayru","manūʿan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,850],[2,850,1610],[3,1610,2460],[4,2460,3925]]}},{"name":"70:22","price":"但し、礼拝する者たちは別だが。¹","arabic":"إِلَّا ٱلۡمُصَلِّينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5397,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　彼らは礼拝の遵守ゆえ、現世においては慎ましい人間となった者たちである。彼らは、現世での悪い出来事に取り乱すこともなく、善い物事に対して強欲になることもない（イブン・ジュザイ２：４８６ー４８７参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"illā al-muṣalīna ","translations":["Except","those who pray ","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","al-muṣalīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,530],[2,530,3765]]}},{"name":"70:23","price":"（彼らは、）自らの礼拝を常々（守りつつ、）行う者たち。","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ دَآئِمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5398,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna hum ʿalā ṣalātihim dāimūna ","translations":["Those who","[they]","at","their prayer","(are) constant","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","hum","ʿalā","ṣalātihim","dāimūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1220],[2,1220,1560],[3,1560,2050],[4,2050,3430],[5,3430,7895]]}},{"name":"70:24","price":"また、自らの財産の内に、（施しのための）一定の権利¹がある者たち、","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ فِيٓ أَمۡوَٰلِهِمۡ حَقّٞ مَّعۡلُومٞ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5399,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この「権利」については、撒き散らすもの章１９の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna fī amwālihim ḥaqqun maʿlūmun ","translations":["And those who","in","their wealth","(is) a right","known","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","fī","amwālihim","ḥaqqun","maʿlūmun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1170],[2,1170,2820],[3,2820,4090],[4,4090,4770],[5,4770,8485]]}},{"name":"70:25","price":"（人々に施しを）要求する者にも、（それを）禁じられた者¹に対しても。","arabic":"لِّلسَّآئِلِ وَٱلۡمَحۡرُومِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5400,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　「禁じられた者」については、撒き散らすもの章１９の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"lilssāili wal-maḥrūmi ","translations":["For the one who asks","and the deprived","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["lilssāili","wal-maḥrūmi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2780],[2,2780,6375]]}},{"name":"70:26","price":"また、報いの日*を信じ（、正しい行い*によってそれに備える）る者たち。","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ يُصَدِّقُونَ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5401,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna yuṣaddiqūna biyawmi al-dīni ","translations":["And those who","accept (the) truth","(of the) Day","(of) the Judgment","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","yuṣaddiqūna","biyawmi","al-dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1200],[2,1200,2510],[3,2510,3360],[4,3360,5925]]}},{"name":"70:27","price":"また、自らの主*の懲罰に、怯える者たち。","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم مِّنۡ عَذَابِ رَبِّهِم مُّشۡفِقُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5402,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum min ʿadhābi rabbihim mush'fiqūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","of","(the) punishment","(of) their Lord","(are) fearful ","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","min","ʿadhābi","rabbihim","mush'fiqūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1200],[2,1200,1560],[3,1560,2630],[4,2630,3430],[5,3430,4850],[6,4850,8745]]}},{"name":"70:28","price":"——本当に彼らの主*の懲罰は、（誰も）安心していられるものではないのだから——。","arabic":"إِنَّ عَذَابَ رَبِّهِمۡ غَيۡرُ مَأۡمُونٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5403,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"inna ʿadhāba rabbihim ghayru mamūnin ","translations":["Indeed","(the) punishment","(of) your Lord","(is) not","to be felt secure (of) ","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","ʿadhāba","rabbihim","ghayru","mamūnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,1890],[3,1890,2820],[4,2820,3470],[5,3470,6505]]}},{"name":"70:29","price":"また、自らの陰部を（禁じられた物事¹から）守る者たち。","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِفُرُوجِهِمۡ حَٰفِظُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5404,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この「禁じられた物事」については、御光章３０の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum lifurūjihim ḥāfiẓūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","their modesty","(are) guardians","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","lifurūjihim","ḥāfiẓūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1100],[2,1100,1490],[3,1490,2880],[4,2880,5955]]}},{"name":"70:30","price":"但し、自分の妻たち、あるいは自分の右手が所有するもの（奴隷*女性）は別で、本当に彼ら（合法な物事だけを行う者たち）は咎められ者などではない。","arabic":"إِلَّا عَلَىٰٓ أَزۡوَٰجِهِمۡ أَوۡ مَا مَلَكَتۡ أَيۡمَٰنُهُمۡ فَإِنَّهُمۡ غَيۡرُ مَلُومِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5405,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"illā ʿalā azwājihim aw mā malakat aymānuhum fa-innahum ghayru malūmīna ","translations":["Except","from","their spouses","or","what","they possess","rightfully","then indeed, they","(are) not","blameworthy","(30)"],"transliterationArr":["illā","ʿalā","azwājihim","aw","mā","malakat","aymānuhum","fa-innahum","ghayru","malūmīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,800],[2,800,2980],[3,2980,4420],[4,4420,4790],[5,4790,5170],[6,5170,5970],[7,5970,7340],[8,7340,9170],[9,9170,9750],[10,9750,12705]]}},{"name":"70:31","price":"誰であろうとそれ以上を欲する者、それらの者たちこそは（アッラー*の法の）違反者なのだ。","arabic":"فَمَنِ ٱبۡتَغَىٰ وَرَآءَ ذَٰلِكَ فَأُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡعَادُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5406,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"famani ib'taghā warāa dhālika fa-ulāika humu al-ʿādūna ","translations":["But whoever","seeks","beyond","that","then those","[they]","(are) the transgressors ","(31)"],"transliterationArr":["famani","ib'taghā","warāa","dhālika","fa-ulāika","humu","al-ʿādūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1440],[3,1440,3500],[4,3500,4240],[5,4240,6759],[6,6759,7099],[7,7099,10094]]}},{"name":"70:32","price":"また、自らの信託と契約を厳守する¹者たち。","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِأَمَٰنَٰتِهِمۡ وَعَهۡدِهِمۡ رَٰعُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5407,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　同様のアーヤ*である、信仰者たち章８の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum li-amānātihim waʿahdihim rāʿūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","of their trusts","and their promise","(are) observers","(32)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","li-amānātihim","waʿahdihim","rāʿūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,1540],[3,1540,3340],[4,3340,4420],[5,4420,7235]]}},{"name":"70:33","price":"また自らの証言を（改変も隠蔽もなく）遂行する者たち。","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم بِشَهَٰدَٰتِهِمۡ قَآئِمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5408,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum bishahādātihim qāimūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","in their testimonies","stand firm","(33)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","bishahādātihim","qāimūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1160],[2,1160,2060],[3,2060,3940],[4,3940,8905]]}},{"name":"70:34","price":"また、自分たちの礼拝を固守する者たち。","arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ يُحَافِظُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5409,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-alladhīna hum ʿalā ṣalātihim yuḥāfiẓūna ","translations":["And those who","[they]","on","their prayer","keep a guard ","(34)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-alladhīna","hum","ʿalā","ṣalātihim","yuḥāfiẓūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,1600],[3,1600,2180],[4,2180,3350],[5,3350,7065]]}},{"name":"70:35","price":"それらの者たちは天国で、厚遇される者たちである。","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ فِي جَنَّٰتٖ مُّكۡرَمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5410,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ulāika fī jannātin muk'ramūna ","translations":["Those","(will be) in","Gardens","honored","(35)"],"transliterationArr":["ulāika","fī","jannātin","muk'ramūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2530],[2,2530,2900],[3,2900,4920],[4,4920,8705]]}},{"name":"70:36","price":"（使徒*よ、）不信仰に陥った者*たちが、あなたに、向かってあたふたとやって来るのは、どうしたことか？¹","arabic":"فَمَالِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ قِبَلَكَ مُهۡطِعِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5411,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　一説にこのアーヤ*は、預言者*の言葉を聞き、嘲笑（ちょうしょう）し、噓呼ばわりするため、彼のもとに集まって来た不信仰者*たちの集団に関して下った（アル＝バガウィー５：１５４参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"famāli alladhīna kafarū qibalaka muh'ṭiʿīna ","translations":["So what is with","those who","disbelieve","before you","(they) hasten","(36)"],"transliterationArr":["famāli","alladhīna","kafarū","qibalaka","muh'ṭiʿīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,790],[2,790,1700],[3,1700,2520],[4,2520,3390],[5,3390,6335]]}},{"name":"70:37","price":"右から左から、三々五々に？","arabic":"عَنِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ وَعَنِ ٱلشِّمَالِ عِزِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5412,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿani al-yamīni waʿani al-shimāli ʿizīna ","translations":["On","the right","and on","the left","(in) separate groups","(37)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿani","al-yamīni","waʿani","al-shimāli","ʿizīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,1420],[3,1420,1990],[4,1990,2950],[5,2950,5635]]}},{"name":"70:38","price":"一体、彼ら（不信仰者*たち）の内のいずれの者も、安寧の楽園に入られることを所望しているというのか？¹","arabic":"أَيَطۡمَعُ كُلُّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ أَن يُدۡخَلَ جَنَّةَ نَعِيمٖ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5413,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　彼らは、「彼ら（ムスリム*たち）が天国に入るのであれば、必ずや私たちこそが、彼らよりも先にそこに入るであろう。そして彼らがそこから何か授かるのなら、必ずや私たちこそが、それより多くのものを授かるだろう」などと言ったものだった（アル＝クルトゥビー１８：２９４参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ayaṭmaʿu kullu im'ri-in min'hum an yud'khala jannata naʿīmin ","translations":["Does long","every","person","among them","that","he enters","a Garden","(of) Delight","(38)"],"transliterationArr":["ayaṭmaʿu","kullu","im'ri-in","min'hum","an","yud'khala","jannata","naʿīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1040],[2,1040,1600],[3,1600,2250],[4,2250,3800],[5,3800,5730],[6,5730,7380],[7,7380,10085]]}},{"name":"70:39","price":"断じて（、そんなことは絶対にあり得）ない！本当にわれら*は彼らが知っているもの¹から、彼らを創ったのだから。","arabic":"كَلَّآۖ إِنَّا خَلَقۡنَٰهُم مِّمَّا يَعۡلَمُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5414,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　彼ら以外の者たちと同じ、しがない一滴の精液から創られたのだから、天国に入るに値するほど高貴な存在だなどと考えるのではない、ということ（ムヤッサル５６９頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"kallā innā khalaqnāhum mimmā yaʿlamūna ","translations":["By no means","Indeed, We","[We] have created them","from what","they know","(39)"],"transliterationArr":["kallā","innā","khalaqnāhum","mimmā","yaʿlamūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,970],[2,970,3170],[3,3170,4490],[4,4490,6550],[5,6550,9785]]}},{"name":"70:40","price":"われはまさに、いくつもの東と、いくつもの西¹において誓う²。本当にわれら*はまさしく、可能な者なのである、","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِرَبِّ ٱلۡمَشَٰرِقِ وَٱلۡمَغَٰرِبِ إِنَّا لَقَٰدِرُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5415,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　ここでの「いくつもの束」と「いくつもの西」は、同年において毎日異なる、太陽の昇る地点と沈む地点のこととされる（アル＝バガウィー４：２６参照）。 ２　この誓いについては、整列者章１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"falā uq'simu birabbi al-mashāriqi wal-maghāribi innā laqādirūna ","translations":["But nay","I swear","by (the) Lord","(of) the risings","and the settings","that We","(are) surely Able","(40)"],"transliterationArr":["falā","uq'simu","birabbi","al-mashāriqi","wal-maghāribi","innā","laqādirūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1860],[2,1860,2690],[3,2690,3440],[4,3440,4650],[5,4650,5970],[6,5970,7440],[7,7440,10645]]}},{"name":"70:41","price":"彼らよりも（アッラー*に服従する）善い者たちを、（彼らの）代わりとすることが。そしてわれらは、出し抜かれる者などではない。","arabic":"عَلَىٰٓ أَن نُّبَدِّلَ خَيۡرٗا مِّنۡهُمۡ وَمَا نَحۡنُ بِمَسۡبُوقِينَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5416,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalā an nubaddila khayran min'hum wamā naḥnu bimasbūqīna ","translations":["[On]","to","[We] replace","(with) better","than them","and not","We","(are) to be outrun","(41)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalā","an","nubaddila","khayran","min'hum","wamā","naḥnu","bimasbūqīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1960],[2,1960,2310],[3,2310,3890],[4,3890,4530],[5,4530,6210],[6,6210,6760],[7,6760,7370],[8,7370,10855]]}},{"name":"70:42","price":"ならば（使徒*よ）、彼らを放っておけ。彼らは、自分たちが（懲罰¹を）約束されている日に遭遇するまで、（虚妄の中に）のめり込み、（宗教において）戯れるであろう。","arabic":"فَذَرۡهُمۡ يَخُوضُواْ وَيَلۡعَبُواْ حَتَّىٰ يُلَٰقُواْ يَوۡمَهُمُ ٱلَّذِي يُوعَدُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5417,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この「懲罰」については、金の装飾章８３の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fadharhum yakhūḍū wayalʿabū ḥattā yulāqū yawmahumu alladhī yūʿadūna ","translations":["So leave them","(to) converse vainly","and amuse themselves","until","they meet","their Day","which","they are promised","(42)"],"transliterationArr":["fadharhum","yakhūḍū","wayalʿabū","ḥattā","yulāqū","yawmahumu","alladhī","yūʿadūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,2130],[3,2130,3210],[4,3210,4030],[5,4030,5020],[6,5020,6070],[7,6070,6950],[8,6950,10115]]}},{"name":"70:43","price":"まるで（アッラー*を差しおいて崇めるために）立てられたもの¹へと急ぐように、彼らが墓場から慌てて出て来る日に（遭遇するまで）。","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَخۡرُجُونَ مِنَ ٱلۡأَجۡدَاثِ سِرَاعٗا كَأَنَّهُمۡ إِلَىٰ نُصُبٖ يُوفِضُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5418,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"１　この「立てられたもの」については、食卓章３の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"yawma yakhrujūna mina al-ajdāthi sirāʿan ka-annahum ilā nuṣubin yūfiḍūna ","translations":["(The) Day","they will come out","from","the graves","rapidly","as if they (were)","to","a goal","hastening","(43)"],"transliterationArr":["yawma","yakhrujūna","mina","al-ajdāthi","sirāʿan","ka-annahum","ilā","nuṣubin","yūfiḍūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,690],[2,690,1770],[3,1770,2140],[4,2140,3350],[5,3350,4950],[6,4950,6910],[7,6910,7510],[8,7510,8950],[9,8950,12385]]}},{"name":"70:44","price":"怖気づいた目をし、屈辱が彼らを覆う。それが（現世で）、彼らに約束されていた日なのである。","arabic":"خَٰشِعَةً أَبۡصَٰرُهُمۡ تَرۡهَقُهُمۡ ذِلَّةٞۚ ذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡيَوۡمُ ٱلَّذِي كَانُواْ يُوعَدُونَ","category":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij"],"ayahNumber":5419,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"khāshiʿatan abṣāruhum tarhaquhum dhillatun dhālika al-yawmu alladhī kānū yūʿadūna ","translations":["Humbled","their eyesights","will cover them","humiliation","That","(is) the Day","which","they were","promised","(44)"],"transliterationArr":["khāshiʿatan","abṣāruhum","tarhaquhum","dhillatun","dhālika","al-yawmu","alladhī","kānū","yūʿadūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,2620],[3,2620,3740],[4,3740,5200],[5,5200,6050],[6,6050,6780],[7,6780,7800],[8,7800,8750],[9,8750,14165]]}}],"chapter":["70 (Al-Ma'arij)","Al-Ma'arij","Surah Al-Ma'arij","Chapter Al-Ma'arij","Ma'arij","Surah Ma'arij","Chapter Ma'arij","Al Ma'arij","Surah Al Ma'arij","Chapter Al Ma'arij","Surah 70","Chapter 70","The Ascending Stairways","المعارج"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}